---
title: Pea and Asparagus Gnocchi with Brown Butter, Tarragon, and Parmesan
description: Gnocchi and brown butter are a match made in flavor heaven! A creamy tarragon-scented sauce brings a light anise flavor to the dish that's perfect with crisp asparagus and sweet peas. This dish is so speedy, maybe you'll even have time to make dessert!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56ddf4e4fd2cb9b3238b4568.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/56ddf4e4fd2cb9b3238b4568.pdf
